                            <comment id="15258122" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 26 Apr 2016 13:57:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 8162ba4534af12879a2da03d4c4d3239a6d3a8fb in lucene-solr&apos;s branch refs/heads/branch_6x from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=noble.paul&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;noble.paul&quot;&gt;noble.paul&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
